Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How does one come to know the unknowable?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"What faculties must a man possess?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.99,0:01:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Since it was discovered that whale oil could light our cities in ways never achieved before,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"it created global demand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"It has pushed man to venture further and further
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.30,0:01:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"into the deep blue unknown.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"We know not its depths,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"nor the host of creatures that live there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.68,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Monsters.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Are they real?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.69,0:01:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Or do the stories exist only to make us respect the sea's dark secrets?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"The question both vexes and excites me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.97,0:02:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"and is the reason I've written you a second time to request a meeting.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.39,0:02:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"A conversation with you, sir, I believe will serve me well for the novel I intend to write,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"currently entitled Moby Dick.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"I hope you will reconsider my offer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"The unknown.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"That is where my imagination yearns to venture.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"And so the question plagues me still.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"How does a man come to know the unknowable?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Sincerely, Herman Melville."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're closed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No boarders after 8:00.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You came.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Someone here for you, my love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tom Nickerson?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Herman Melville.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We received your letter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.54,0:03:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're either a desperate man or a fool to come all the way to Nantucket.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, my offer still stands.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Three months' lodgings for a single night's talk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All I have in the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I prefer to think of it as an investment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I want you to tell me what happened to the Essex.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you think happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There are rumblings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Rumors that the Essex was... - What do you want?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What story do you expect to hear?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That of the whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex ran aground. There was a full inquiry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I believe the inquiry was less than truthful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You are the last survivor of the Essex, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you won't talk, who will?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Leave. Now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- No. You mustn't go. Please. - He is in no mind to talk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And I haven't come all this way to be humiliated and waste my time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, Mr. Melville.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He won't talk about the Essex to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To anyone. Never has. Never.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's an agony about him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,His soul
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,is in torment,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and in need of confession.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, just let me talk to him. Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I believe it would do you good to talk to the man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You listen well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.57,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who holds this place together while you drink yourself to death?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.66,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You will talk with this man as much as is necessary to keep the money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.25,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know our circumstances, Thomas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Only as much as is necessary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll get whiskey.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I neglected to mention it in my letter, but I was a whaler once.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,One trip, I mean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Green hand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, you've seen it all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My wife read your books.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She enjoyed them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm happy to hear it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've had good sales.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And I think this story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,could surpass the success of even my first novel,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which did quite well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Another of your seafaring yarns?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Have you read Hawthorne, Mr. Melville?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now there's a writer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Great writer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But he is not here. And I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For my own particular reasons.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I will tell you of the Essex.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I believe you will be disappointed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But every word I say will be true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Story of the Essex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,is the story of two men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain George Pollard
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and his first mate,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You don't wanna be late.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll be there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Besides, can't have our daughter sleeping under a leaky roof, can we?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What makes you so sure it's a girl?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, it has to be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So she can remind me why I still love you when you're being stubborn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, if it's to be a daughter, she'll be a version of you, not me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Blond locks and determined to conquer the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I suppose after today, you'll be trading in that tunic for a uniform.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.14,0:08:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's right. Finally out of this patch of dirt, into a captain's house like you deserve.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't need one of those houses in town with stuffy neighbors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's plenty of room here for the three of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know, sometimes your kind heart and good nature
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,is just unbearable.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Go get your captaincy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- What's your bid? - I'll have $1.90.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I've got 1,000 gallons at $2! - I'll take 40 shares!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Seller! Seller! Over here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Criterion's back with a fine haul. 1,600 barrels.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.88,0:09:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A new record. 50 pounds sterling for head matter on the London market.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Congratulations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Good morning, Mr. Chase. - Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come in, please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My partner, Benjamin Fuller.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do sit down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do hope you realize how satisfied we are
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,with the work you've done for us over the years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, one of our ships, the Essex,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.97,0:10:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,has just been refitted at great expense and is to go to sea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.85,0:10:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, having made such an investment in her, we want to be sure she's in the best possible hands.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it gives us great pleasure to offer you a position aboard her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As first mate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As first mate?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Mason, you promised me command of a ship after my last voyage
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,when I brought you back 1,500 barrels. Do you remember? You gave me your word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That promise must now be deferred.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like everyone else, we've had a lean time recently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.84,0:10:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, never on my watch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.13,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nantucket now dominates the world market.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That must not change.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is no time for experimentation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex will be captained by George Pollard,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,scion of a great whaling family.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,His father also happens to be our patron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Blood, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can have all the voyages under your belt you want,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but blood will always win out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, well, blood is not gonna fill a ship with oil, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.75,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To successfully command, a captain needs respect. Now, what if the men don't respect him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You will make sure that they do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, good day, gentlemen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I understand your disappointment,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so, a one-fifteenth lay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's more than I've ever paid any first officer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.93,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And if you bring back 2,000 barrels of oil, I give you my word,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,next time, you will have your captaincy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You've given me your word before, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, this time, I'll take it in writing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We've just had a most agreeable conversation with Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He'll be honored to serve under you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now I'm to babysit a greenhorn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.98,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Some chinless Nantucketer born with a damn silver spoon in his mouth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know, I should've thrown the offer back in their faces.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why? You now have the offer of command in writing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, well, a liar's word is worthless, even on paper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know, I'd love you just as much if you were a merchant captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you wouldn't be gone for two years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I won't be gone two years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A Bedford whaler came back last week who was gone three.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She lost two men and still with her hull half empty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, well, they were from Bedford, and they didn't have me on board.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I will captain my own ship!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A whaling ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Up to them, all we'd ever have is this patch of dirt, and that's not gonna happen, Peggy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Those are your father's words, not yours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's wrong with his words?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He wanted things for his family, for himself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He was a dreamer, Owen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, he was.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dreamed of the sea and never got to sail it because of men like them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,At least he got to see his children born.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's all I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I married a whaleman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll come back as quick as a summer's night, I swear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just come back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Promise me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I already swore to you. Now you want me to promise, too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I promise.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Son, a word With you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To be a captain, you cannot be a friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You are their superior.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Never forget that. Never let them forget that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.14,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Your great-grandfather and a few others created this industry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.60,0:15:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Without us, without you, the world plunges into darkness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.15,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hope to bring honor to the Pollard family name, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.74,0:15:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Thou didst, O Lord, create the mighty whale
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"That wondrous monster of a mighty length
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Beyond conception his unmeasured strength
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"But, everlasting God, thou dost ordain
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"That we, poor feeble mortals should engage
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Ourselves, our wives and children to maintain
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"This dreadful monster with a martial rage"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.44,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,O Father, grant that your glorious light shine on these men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ensure them a prosperous voyage,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that they may return safely and with a full ship,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so that the white flames of Nantucket whale oil
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,may continue to keep light in our homes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,city streets safe from sin in the night,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and to fuel the machines of industry
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that drive our great nation forward
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,as our noble species evolves.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In your name, we pray.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.02,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,what month was this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Late in the year.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We were one of the last ships to go out,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which is why my friend Barzillai and I got a berth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.12,0:16:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I was 14. Fourteen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, you're standing around, boy. Move!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,First time to sea. Scared,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but more scared to show it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Barzillai was 17.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Orphans. Grew up on the wharf.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Both in a hurry to be called men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Grubs, what are those pins they're wearing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They're whale pins, Thomas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do I get one of them?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, you gotta thrust the killing lance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Into the largest beast that ever breathed on this Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, get the green stuff to Mr. Bond, there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make it quick, damn it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I shall have 12 of those one day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Windlass is ready and sails are loose, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy, this is only half my order!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Put them over the ground tier casks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, well, you being on board means only one thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, at least there's one person on this ship who knows the truth about Owen Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, that all the other ships have already crewed up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, now. I'm a reformed man, Owen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Question is, are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't tell me Matthew Joy's put down the bottle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dry as sand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Has Owen Chase put down his temper?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, serene as the church.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll believe that when I see it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And given our captain,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll give your serenity about
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,48 hours?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pollard. George Pollard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Chase." That's an off-island name, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And very shortly, we will be off-island for some time, and I'll be very much at home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Must say I was surprised.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Normally, a captain gets to choose his first mate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,An experienced captain, yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.69,0:18:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you can understand from the owners' point of view, they want to feel their investment's in the hands of men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Indeed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They probably want a little extra reassurance, that's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, do keep an eye on me and let me know if I'm doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, I know no other way, Captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, haul short the anchor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yank to the wind! There's topmen aloft.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Aye! - Mr. Lawrence, take the helm. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy, make sail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Cole! Mr. Chappel! Stand by the spanker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set your fore staysail and your fore and main topsails.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Come on, look lively, you lads. - Come on, Nickerson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,While we're young! Let fall clews and bunts and sheet ho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set topsails and topgallants. Heave away on the windlass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Heave away on the windlass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.99,0:19:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set topgallants. Let go clew lines and sheet ho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's a snarl in the gasket, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chappel, take the helm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It won't clear, Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.58,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on! Why aren't those braces laid out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Mr. Ray, where are my headsails? - Aye, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Crank away on the windlass!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Crank away on the windlass, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, pull!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make sail, God damn it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God and all of Nantucket is watching, men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anchor's trim!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain! Head down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mind your head, Captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.74,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's the matter, Mr. Sheppard?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gasket's fouled the sheet, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It won't clear, Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.99,0:20:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Topgallant sheet is jammed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The gasket still won't clear!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We don't have enough sail on yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Still won't clear!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Watch your step!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's the gasket, Owen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stand clear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whoa! Bloody hell!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let fall your course!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Heave!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make fast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.51,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nice piece of work, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.32,0:21:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we make Cape Verdes in the next two weeks, we'll have a decent chance of reaching the Pacific on schedule.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Corn, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, no, thank you, sir. Never did have much of a taste for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's odd.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Told your father grew corn on Cape Cod.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.88,0:21:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's right. He did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As you can imagine, I certainly grew tired of eating it every day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.09,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Corn. Okra. Beans, I believe?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Before he went to jail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you familiar with this story, Mr. Joy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Were you aware that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase was effectively orphaned due to his father's incarceration?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, we all have our own paths to sea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.53,0:22:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As a rule, we tend not to ask too many questions.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hmm. Can't have been easy, though. Yet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you had Nantucket's great seafaring family to adopt you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.13,0:22:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is far from the first time I've been called a landsman or an off-islander
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.42,0:22:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,by some Nantucketer, reminding me how I am not a part of that family.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, if the Captain will excuse me, there are whaleboats and watches to assign.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.65,0:22:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, sir. Not for me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.86,0:22:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Not a drop? - No, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.44,0:22:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like I said,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.28,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sometimes the fewer questions one asks, the better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Serve that food up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Getting this slop on the first day?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cheap bastards. Where's the meat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.43,0:23:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's a gorgeous girl, Mr. Chappel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.97,0:23:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A vision of beauty, that. Carved on a varnished whale bone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Let me have a touch. - Don't touch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.31,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I thought you were married, anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.89,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am, and there she is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, that's her nose, anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.57,0:23:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Congratulations, ladies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.65,0:23:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That was a fine job trimming sails today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.91,0:23:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A sorrier pack of deck wallopers I don't think I've ever seen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.79,0:23:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chappel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.12,0:23:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.12,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're Captain's harpooner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence, you'll be mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.46,0:23:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And Mr. Peterson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Second mate's harpooner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.22,0:23:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.38,0:23:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There'll be six men to a boat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.47,0:23:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,First drills are tomorrow. Six bells sharp.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're not even east of Halifax, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's your name?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Coffin. Henry Coffin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's the Captain's cousin, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.73,0:24:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, well, Mr. Coffin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.65,0:24:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You think a whale knows if it's east of Halifax?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.53,0:24:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't know who all of you are or how you got here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.24,0:24:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Some of you probably have felonies to hide and you're on the run.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's fine. I don't give a damn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But in return, you exist for one thing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.71,0:24:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and one thing only.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.26,0:24:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And that is whale oil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.13,0:24:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I intend to fill our 2,000 barrels and be home as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.68,0:24:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And even when the weather is fine and there are no whales, Mr. Coffin,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.10,0:24:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we will lower the boats and practice all maneuvers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.35,0:24:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,necessary in the capture of a whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.85,0:24:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And any man who is idle will find himself swimming home. Is that understood?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.32,0:24:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Greenhorn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.53,0:24:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,On deck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.74,0:25:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,On you go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.79,0:25:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, aye, landsman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.25,0:25:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Thomas Nickerson, right? - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.30,0:25:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know, some feel sick at first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.68,0:25:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, pull me back up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.22,0:25:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Best way to square it with King Neptune, boy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.72,0:25:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please bring me up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.48,0:25:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Better now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.86,0:25:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.07,0:25:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.90,0:25:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, now you got something to write home to your mother about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.99,0:25:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My mother's buried up in Smith's Hill.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.83,0:25:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's a stone for my father, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.08,0:25:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He was lost at sea before I was born.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.09,0:25:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here, give me that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.38,0:25:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, this is your family now, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.72,0:25:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For better or for worse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Worse, mostly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.64,0:26:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Swab the deck, kid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.70,0:26:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dogwatch! You're gonna learn what it takes to be Whalers today, mates.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.87,0:26:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.75,0:26:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- You led that line wrong, Nickerson. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.59,0:26:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- We'll stay at this till sundown if we have to. - Aye, Mr. Joy, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.63,0:26:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Main topsail leech lines!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.13,0:26:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Harpooner, make ready to boat!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.84,0:26:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Aye, sir! - Aye, Mr. Joy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.93,0:26:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Go main topsail leech lines. Too slow, you damn coofs!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.85,0:26:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The bailing piggins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.22,0:26:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You will learn every inch of this ship before you return to your bunks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.52,0:26:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sweat that line, Barz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.73,0:26:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- You need to move quicker, Mr. Ray. - Aye, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.86,0:26:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ain't no greenhorns no more, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.28,0:27:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're a sailor now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.70,0:27:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not bad, Mr. Ray. Well done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.83,0:27:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Forecourse bunts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.50,0:27:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get used to it, lads. You're gonna work like horses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.42,0:27:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.79,0:27:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.71,0:27:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set stunsails.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.96,0:27:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is that wise, sir? We're nearing the Gulf Stream. Best keep it five knots till we can see the weather.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.05,0:27:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are two days behind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.30,0:27:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We need to make up the time if we're to catch the easterlies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.39,0:27:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set stunsails.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.48,0:27:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Set stunsails. Come on, move. - Aye, Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.98,0:27:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Belay that! Set stunsails!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.70,0:27:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get aloft, Mr. Coffin. The captain wants speed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.41,0:27:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look for braces, lads. Trim for speed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.08,0:27:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Set fore the main topsail and topgallant stunsails, men. Move it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.25,0:27:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make fast your stunsail halyard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.17,0:27:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make fast stunsail halyard, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.92,0:27:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stunsail boom ready, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.80,0:28:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bracing fore topsail, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.30,0:28:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.82,0:28:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- The captain's got us moving now! - We're finally getting somewhere!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.95,0:28:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She may be old, but she can still roll, boys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.13,0:28:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, a squall on the starboard bow. We must shorten sail immediately.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.01,0:28:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not just yet, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.18,0:28:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, we are headed into a squall at more than 8 knots, and it's moving faster than that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.01,0:28:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let it come. The men are soft from months on land. They need a good baptism. Let them know our work has begun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.73,0:28:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we don't shorten sail and bear off, it'll catch us on the beam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.53,0:29:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.19,0:29:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we will stand on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.95,0:29:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence? Hold our course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.82,0:29:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Holding course, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.28,0:29:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll lose half a day running like that. We'll skirt the edge of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.70,0:29:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If the men can't handle a gust like this, then God help us all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.26,0:29:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Best secure for heavy weather.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.18,0:29:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rough weather coming up, boys. Get this deck secure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.81,0:29:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Double gripes on the boats!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.24,0:29:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Best prepare for weather, Mr. Bond. We're headed into a squall.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.99,0:29:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Secure the main hatch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.70,0:29:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's moving fast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.51,0:30:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We must fall off and run with it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.85,0:30:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We will stand on, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.89,0:30:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence! Hold your course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.39,0:30:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Holding course, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.86,0:30:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sea's coming aboard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.20,0:30:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.28,0:30:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shorten sail, Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.20,0:30:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Climb to weather and grab the shrouds!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.58,0:30:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Climb to weather! Get to windward and hold on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.58,0:30:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We need to get those sails down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.42,0:30:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Go lee!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.84,0:30:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, hold fast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.18,0:30:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold steady lines!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.06,0:30:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold fast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.90,0:31:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Turn the ship! Turn to leeward!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.61,0:31:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No! The damage is done!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.69,0:31:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Strike topgallants. Let fly sheets! - No, turn the ship!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.07,0:31:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Veer off, Mr. Lawrence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:09.11,0:31:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's too late! It's too goddamn late!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.41,0:31:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- We'll be broadsided! - Turn this ship!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.25,0:31:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Hold on! - Turn!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.13,0:31:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Strike those damn topgallants!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.30,0:31:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.58,0:32:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.98,0:32:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.57,0:32:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- We have to cut away the topgallants! - Topgallants away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.03,0:32:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have to get her upright!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.67,0:33:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You wish to see me, sir?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.34,0:33:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,At six bells tomorrow,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.76,0:33:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you will assemble the crew.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.93,0:33:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Inform them that we will be returning to Nantucket for repairs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.85,0:33:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You will then apologize to them for interfering with a captain's order,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.10,0:33:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which nearly cost the lives of every man on this ship today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.60,0:33:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.44,0:33:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll accept your resignation upon our return to port. That will be all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.11,0:33:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- It was your order to set stunsails, sir. - That decision was sound.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.61,0:33:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The men needed testing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:55.61,0:33:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- So you send them into a storm? - That...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.53,0:34:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- That was unlucky. - No, it was bad seamanship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.29,0:34:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And blaming misfortune is just plain weakness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.95,0:34:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Damn your impertinence!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.75,0:34:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you know who you're speaking to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.92,0:34:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My name is Captain George Pollard. Pollard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.09,0:34:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you, Mr. Chase, no matter how many whale pins you may have on your lapel,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.26,0:34:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,are nothing more than the son of a farmer
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:21.64,0:34:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,who's managed to bully his way into an officer's tunic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.27,0:34:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now get out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.07,0:34:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To return to port without a single barrel of oil would be a mistake, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.99,0:34:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And not behoove a man whose name is Pollard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.95,0:34:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Or Chase, for that matter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.41,0:34:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And the best thing for both of us would be to work all hours God sends us,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.62,0:34:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,fill this ship with oil and be home inside a year
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.46,0:34:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and rid of one another as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.13,0:34:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Trust me, I am every bit as desirous of that as you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.84,0:35:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course, that is a captain's decision.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.11,0:35:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They were like an ill-married couple.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.20,0:35:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,An ill-married couple will tolerate each other, Mr. Melville.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.20,0:35:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But an ill-married couple can also bring down a ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.54,0:35:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you married, Mr. Melville?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.87,0:35:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.16,0:35:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God have mercy on you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.71,0:35:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,First child on the way, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.38,0:35:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, does your good wife know that you've brought all you have in the world here tonight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:36.55,0:35:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and given it to a stranger?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.38,0:35:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.72,0:35:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're full of surprises, aren't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.55,0:35:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.81,0:35:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,the Essex did not return to port.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.81,0:35:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She did not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.31,0:35:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She continued out to sea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.81,0:35:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, she did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.15,0:35:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And before long, we heard that call that all whalemen pray for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.57,0:36:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Blows."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.37,0:36:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Blows!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.58,0:36:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To windward! There she blows!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.20,0:36:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right or sperm, Mr. Ramsdell?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.83,0:36:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sperm whales they are!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.25,0:36:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There go the flukes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:15.29,0:36:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase! Hoist and swing boats.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.26,0:36:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All hands! All hands on deck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.55,0:36:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All hands on deck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.01,0:36:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Away the boats.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.27,0:36:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lower away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.96,0:36:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Straight! Crack them backbones.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.46,0:37:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.96,0:37:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Give way all. Spring those oars till your arms fall off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.56,0:37:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There they breach!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.93,0:37:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thataway, boys! Full pressure!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.98,0:37:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.60,0:37:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on! Put your back into it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.15,0:37:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pull! Pull like a vengeance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.57,0:37:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There she blows!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.16,0:37:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's a calf.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.25,0:37:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's the calf?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.50,0:37:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's the cow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.80,0:37:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And that's our boy! That's the money.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.97,0:37:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, push!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.18,0:37:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.43,0:37:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Forty-barreler?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.93,0:37:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Fifty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.94,0:37:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, he's a buster!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.15,0:37:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bite the oars, lads.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.48,0:38:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Blister your goddamn lungs!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.53,0:38:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Full pressure! Smartly, lads! Smartly!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.95,0:38:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mind your oars!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.03,0:38:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Ramsdell, prepare the line.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.87,0:38:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.33,0:38:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence, the first one's mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.21,0:38:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take me to the pretty spot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.63,0:38:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pull! Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.55,0:38:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stay on him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.40,0:38:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're on your first Nantucket sleigh ride, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.32,0:38:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.08,0:39:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look at him! The most fearsome creature ever to live on this Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.93,0:39:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He sounds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.43,0:39:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My hands!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.61,0:39:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LAWRENCE. We need to wet the line, Nickerson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.41,0:39:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Give way, lads. Give way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.42,0:39:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Got 140 fathoms of line left, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.43,0:39:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Eighty fathoms of line left, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.77,0:40:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's gonna pull us under!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.48,0:40:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Matthew, I need your line!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.15,0:40:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Keep going!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.44,0:40:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Peterson, give me the line.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.73,0:40:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.11,0:40:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Give me that line, Mr. Peterson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.49,0:40:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're down to 60 fathoms of line left, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.49,0:40:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Twenty fathoms, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.95,0:40:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tie it off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.58,0:40:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Safe!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.62,0:40:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:36.51,0:40:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Peterson, lay out. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.68,0:40:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How many fathoms can he go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.35,0:40:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,70 fathoms left, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.77,0:40:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no, no, wait.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.82,0:40:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.66,0:40:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no! Not yet! Don't touch that line!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.20,0:40:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Down to 50 fathoms, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.37,0:41:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen, God damn it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.87,0:41:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I said don't touch it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.50,0:41:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30 fathoms left, Mr. Joy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.46,0:41:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ten fathoms left, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.88,0:41:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Backwater!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.92,0:41:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Push!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.26,0:41:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Chimney's afire!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.06,0:42:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Chimney's afire!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.56,0:42:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Afire!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.59,0:42:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hurry it along, lads.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.59,0:42:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God! Get out, you bastards.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.90,0:42:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Blubber in the Oil. Smell that, boys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.66,0:42:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's us making money!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.12,0:43:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get out of there, you sons of bitches.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.58,0:43:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- There, you got it? - There's not a chance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.92,0:43:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- How's it looking? - It's not good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.76,0:43:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.14,0:43:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.68,0:43:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.01,0:43:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's all of it, sir. We can't get any more out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.43,0:43:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's the gold in there, boys. Come on, keep digging.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.14,0:43:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're too big to wriggle down there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.02,0:43:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then find someone who can.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.45,0:43:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson! Come here, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.78,0:43:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey! I said come here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.00,0:43:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Climb on into him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.87,0:43:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on, Thomas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.54,0:43:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's in there is worth a hell of a lot more than what they're boiling down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.26,0:44:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir! I can't, I'm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.55,0:44:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry. I can't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:06.18,0:44:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You get down there, or I'll have you sleep down there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:11.90,0:44:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You best put that between your teeth, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.52,0:44:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stinks worse than the devil's asshole down there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.90,0:44:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.54,0:44:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:28.58,0:44:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here, Nickerson, take my pillow with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:33.88,0:44:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Down you go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.27,0:44:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A man gets to know himself down there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:56.27,0:44:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They ever send you into a whale's head?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.19,0:44:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.11,0:45:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I was spared.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:01.78,0:45:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, that's where the treasure is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:06.24,0:45:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll never forget that first bull.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.37,0:45:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Forty-seven barrels. 'Course, the happiness was short-lived.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:15.21,0:45:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- The waters there had all been fished out? - That they had.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:19.92,0:45:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, we headed further out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.14,0:45:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah. Took us a month to round the Horn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.81,0:45:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Left the South Atlantic behind with a sliver of hope
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.10,0:45:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that things could change for the better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:38.11,0:45:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But making the Pacific didn't improve our lot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.65,0:45:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whale sightings were too damn scarce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.66,0:45:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After nearly a year at sea,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:50.91,0:45:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,the temperaments of our captain and first mate grew more strained.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.92,0:45:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard spent most days and nights in his cabin,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:00.75,0:46:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,afraid to look his crew in the eye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.18,0:46:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Our hold was almost empty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.77,0:46:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And to gaze upon our paltry efforts
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.81,0:46:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,only served as a reminder
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.85,0:46:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that we were a long way from going home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.17,0:46:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no. I don't talk that talk. Speak English.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.72,0:46:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Offer me more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:49.55,0:46:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here, sir. This, Nantucket whale oil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.52,0:46:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Ain't no skinny hog worth more than that. - More!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.95,0:47:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Capitan. Excuse me. The locals told me your voyage was waylaid, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.28,0:47:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain George Pollard. The Essex.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.87,0:47:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Capitan Clemente Pelaez, the Santa Maria.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.96,0:48:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Would you buy a colleague a drink?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.22,0:48:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.97,0:48:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bad luck? How far out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:16.26,0:48:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Far enough for only a fool to go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:18.93,0:48:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How far would that be?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.48,0:48:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A thousand leagues along the equator.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:25.11,0:48:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Offshore Grounds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.48,0:48:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Were there whales there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.90,0:48:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More than you've ever dreamed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.45,0:48:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hundreds. Fields of flukes far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.12,0:48:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Could have filled up 3,000 barrels in the space of a day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.46,0:48:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you mean, "could have"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.17,0:48:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If it weren't for that demon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:50.47,0:48:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:52.84,0:48:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White as alabaster. Hundred feet long.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:58.43,0:49:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sent six of my crew to their graves.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.53,0:49:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And the rest of us, something to remember him by.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:13.99,0:49:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, this white whale, did he dance a jig and pick your pocket as well?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:23.12,0:49:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gracias.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.04,0:49:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You believe that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.67,0:49:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we set sail now,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.47,0:49:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,catch the south easterlies at their best time and fill our belly, we could be home in six months.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:41.06,0:49:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What say you, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:43.06,0:49:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No need to endure our predicament for a moment longer than necessary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:46.40,0:49:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Amen to that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.73,0:49:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Amen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:51.32,0:49:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Greed took hold of our captain and first mate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:55.03,0:49:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So we headed out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:57.37,0:49:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A thousand leagues along the equator.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.49,0:50:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where knowledge ended,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.70,0:50:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,speculation began.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.91,0:50:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's where the whales had gone to hide.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.75,0:50:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As far from man as they could possibly go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.25,0:50:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But we hunted them down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.26,0:50:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Centuries before, sailors feared sailing off the edge of the Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:20.76,0:50:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But we were headed for the edge of sanity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:27.60,0:50:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Trust gave way to doubt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:30.57,0:50:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hope to blind superstition.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:33.78,0:50:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain, the men are talking.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.95,0:50:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's what men do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.28,0:50:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They aren't happy with your decision to sail out this far.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.08,0:50:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, did you correct them? Did you remind them of our purpose to fill this ship with whale oil,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:47.04,0:50:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and if the whales are 1,000 leagues out, that that is where we will go?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.13,0:50:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cousin, please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:55.13,0:50:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is madness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:57.97,0:51:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You have let yourself be influenced by that man. You must turn this ship back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.47,0:51:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I suggest you go back down, reassure the men,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.81,0:51:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,be a leader
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:10.31,0:51:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and don't ever, ever abuse the privilege of family with me again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.61,0:51:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Coffin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:48.02,0:51:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:50.02,0:51:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Listen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.02,0:51:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:52.31,0:51:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see some white water.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.52,0:51:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Where? - Portside!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:55.15,0:51:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- We're away! - Portside, Captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:56.57,0:51:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Where are they? - You see anything?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.91,0:52:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lower away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.37,0:52:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lower away! Lower away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:11.54,0:52:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The devil take the Mexican grounds!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.37,0:52:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Peak oars!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:55.13,0:52:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Give it to him, Mr. Chappel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.63,0:53:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stick him, man! Stick him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:05.26,0:53:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dead ahead, Peterson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.27,0:53:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't let him chew your oars, boys.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:20.78,0:53:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Back to it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.76,0:53:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The whale?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.30,0:53:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.97,0:53:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So it's true?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.39,0:53:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.02,0:53:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Too much is true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.64,0:53:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get it up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:11.54,0:54:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Full pressure!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.01,0:54:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Bond!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:29.47,0:54:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Back the foreyard, lower the tackle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.72,0:54:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.18,0:54:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here she comes, Peterson. Now, now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.70,0:54:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence, take us leeward, head us straight for the school.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.04,0:54:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.87,0:54:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hot tar, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:54.91,0:54:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll find him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.04,0:55:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're boat to black skin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.38,0:55:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Beach us on her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:14.72,0:55:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's ours, men!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.09,0:55:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What was that, Mr. Lawrence?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.10,0:55:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.77,0:56:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God damn it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:05.78,0:56:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Find Mr...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.80,0:56:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Easton!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.78,0:56:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get Mr. Lawrence to man the pumps!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.32,0:56:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where is he?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:54.87,0:56:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Port bow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:08.17,0:57:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get me the biggest irons we have.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.80,0:57:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He wants a fight?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.19,0:57:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Never seen a whale do that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:26.65,0:57:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence, take the wheel. Mr. Ramsdell, secure the other end of the line to the foremast.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:31.32,0:57:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:32.24,0:57:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As I live and breathe, he's mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.58,0:58:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Cut the line! - Look out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.63,0:59:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Captain! - What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:18.30,0:59:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex! She's listing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:32.02,0:59:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Turn this boat around!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:09.89,1:00:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Help me! Mr. Joy! - Nickerson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.85,1:00:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Here! Give me your hand! - Help!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:13.90,1:00:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.35,1:00:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.90,1:00:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A whale, sir. It stove the ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.90,1:00:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.03,1:01:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We lost Easton and Sanborn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.24,1:01:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The pumps are useless, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:14.25,1:01:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Prepare to abandon ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:16.04,1:01:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We can't row our way home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:18.21,1:01:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll have to strip her of her sails and jimmy-rig something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:21.09,1:01:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gather as much food and water as you can carry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.05,1:01:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're gonna need all the fresh water you can find.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:26.60,1:01:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, you grab as much as you can. Barz, come with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.44,1:01:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sweet Lord!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.98,1:01:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,First, the sails, then the provisions.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.44,1:01:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get as much food as you can carry, lad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.61,1:01:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Make haste, boys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.12,1:01:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nickerson, there are more casks in steerage.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:49.28,1:01:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Got it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:50.24,1:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hardtack is dry. Move sprightly, gentlemen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:53.29,1:01:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lower away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.62,1:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Take those tack lines. - Up aloft!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:56.63,1:01:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Lower away! Bring it down! - Mr. Cole, get that yard down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.13,1:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bring it down. Keep it coming!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.84,1:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.10,1:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on, Nickerson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.97,1:02:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get those sails!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.10,1:02:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There you go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.98,1:02:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get that yard down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.82,1:02:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We need the sails. Not enough water.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.70,1:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get the barrels, now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:33.45,1:02:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Strip that rigging!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.96,1:02:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More fresh water! More hardtack! Come on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.17,1:02:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can see more casks in the steerage!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.21,1:02:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Benjamin! Quick! Come on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:41.55,1:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Give me your hand! - Get him up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.01,1:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.51,1:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hardtack!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.80,1:02:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on! Move it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.64,1:02:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Step lively, Mr. Nickerson!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:56.52,1:02:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gotta get away from the oil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:57.85,1:02:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's going down! She's listing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:59.52,1:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's Owen? Nickerson, where is Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.98,1:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He was just here, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:03.86,1:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.07,1:03:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.07,1:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Mr. Chase! - We gotta shove off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.53,1:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on, now, boys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:09.53,1:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oil on deck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.03,1:03:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Captain! - Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.56,1:03:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.35,1:03:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.10,1:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where is the first mate?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:50.86,1:03:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's gonna blow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.95,1:03:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Owen! - We gotta move!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.24,1:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, wait! Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.24,1:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.37,1:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:44.79,1:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There he is! There he is! There he is!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.76,1:04:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:53.47,1:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Move that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:55.47,1:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir. Here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:58.35,1:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get ahold, now. We got you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.98,1:05:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Sir. - You're all right now, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:07.94,1:05:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Going fishing, are we?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:09.36,1:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Clean and load it, Mr. Joy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:23.29,1:05:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Back away, or she'll take us down with her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:10.11,1:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:12.15,1:07:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What about our provisions?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:19.99,1:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Two ounces of hardtack a day per man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:23.45,1:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And half a cup of water.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.96,1:07:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, man, we can't live on that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.63,1:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not for more than a few days.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:49.31,1:07:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's he.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:55.65,1:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, it's him, all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.53,1:08:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You don't fool me, Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:03.62,1:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Coffin?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:04.87,1:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:05.79,1:08:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You put us here. You know you put us here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:10.62,1:08:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Hey! Put it down! - Mr. Coffin, put the pistol down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:12.79,1:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say you're scared!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:13.84,1:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- What are you doing? - Mr. Coffin, put the pistol down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:16.00,1:08:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know what happens when the food and water runs out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:18.47,1:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do as the captain says, Coffin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:20.34,1:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I just wanna see the landsman scared. - Mr. Coffin, put the pistol down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:22.72,1:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- That's an order! - Do as the captain says! Now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:25.35,1:08:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.22,1:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Henry. - Say it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:28.18,1:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:29.73,1:08:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Henry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:31.39,1:08:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Put the pistol down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:37.32,1:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Henry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:39.40,1:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Put it down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.19,1:09:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So east it was.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.73,1:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Back in the direction we'd come.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.74,1:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Though only the sun and compass told us so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:26.91,1:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All directions looked the same.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:29.58,1:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Our hope was to catch the Westerlies to Easter Island.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.21,1:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A journey of 3,000 miles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:37.63,1:09:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In 12 days, we have drifted south.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:39.96,1:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Six degrees latitude.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.63,1:09:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're not one mile closer to Easter Island.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:46.30,1:09:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We stayed in the same place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.64,1:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are cursed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.77,1:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll make up for it when we catch the variables.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:58.40,1:09:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll catch them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:29.89,1:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Chappel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:31.72,1:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Chappel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:33.81,1:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Chappel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:35.14,1:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You've got him, Captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:42.11,1:10:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy, the halyard's jammed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:47.78,1:10:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.45,1:10:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You all right, Mr. Joy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.83,1:10:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Grab the tiller!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.12,1:10:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Grab it! - Matthew!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.88,1:11:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get that sail down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.66,1:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Matthew. Hey, what happened? What happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.71,1:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Owen. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:38.71,1:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Let me take a look. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:40.21,1:11:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lay still. Let me look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.33,1:11:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Owen, I'm fine. All right. - Just relax. Relax. Let me take a look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.42,1:11:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I'm fine! - I know. I know. I just wanna take a look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.26,1:11:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I banged my head. Just a scratch, all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:53.47,1:11:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Just a scratch. - Give him some water.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.97,1:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't need any water!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:56.14,1:11:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Give him some goddamn water!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:58.06,1:12:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no, no. I don't need water. I'm fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:08.24,1:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take that. Take it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:10.70,1:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey. I got you, I got you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:13.20,1:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're all right. You're all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.58,1:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey! What're you all looking at? I'm fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:23.13,1:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard. Fit as a fiddle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:26.00,1:12:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Fit as a goddamned fiddle. You hear me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.05,1:12:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Owen. - Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:30.30,1:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm fine. All right? I'm fine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:34.10,1:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- You're a tough son of a bitch. - Thank you. I'm fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.22,1:12:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get out of here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:38.64,1:12:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.02,1:12:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.65,1:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:46.73,1:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Them two men have known each other,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.32,1:12:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sailed together since childhood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.95,1:12:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, tell me, could you sit there and watch your own brother die?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.87,1:12:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Simply a matter of numbers, Mr. Chappel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.58,1:13:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's not enough for all of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.51,1:13:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.14,1:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.52,1:13:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water? Why waste?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:23.56,1:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water on a dead man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.23,1:13:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Nickerson?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.86,1:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why waste water...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.07,1:13:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You all right, sir?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.95,1:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I cannot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:33.28,1:13:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cannot what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:34.66,1:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:36.28,1:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You have enough. More than enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:38.62,1:13:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But, sir, we've come so far.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.37,1:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have come to an end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.91,1:13:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have an agreement, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.37,1:13:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take the money and leave! The devil's bargain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:46.88,1:13:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, sir. The devil loves unspoken secrets.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:53.93,1:13:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Especially those that fester in a man's soul.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.64,1:14:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's yours?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.24,1:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am not a great writer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.12,1:14:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am not Hawthorne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:27.00,1:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But from my first hearing of it,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:30.00,1:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,this tale has haunted me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:33.67,1:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It consumes me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:36.68,1:14:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I fear if I do not write it,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:40.51,1:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then I should never write again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:43.64,1:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What else?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.85,1:14:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I fear if I do write it,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:50.52,1:14:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that it will not be as good as it should be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.45,1:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Continue the story, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.54,1:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For the both of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:24.85,1:15:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pass that down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:31.23,1:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:37.95,1:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We thank you, Lord, for this is our food.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:41.49,1:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:42.49,1:15:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For life and health, and every good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:46.83,1:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let all manner to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:47.91,1:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Land. Land!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:51.79,1:15:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Land! Land! - Land!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:54.34,1:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Land!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:55.38,1:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Land!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:57.01,1:16:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oars! Give way! Give way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:01.01,1:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oars! Now! Give way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:03.14,1:16:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Row!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:11.98,1:16:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I saw it, Mr. Chase. - That you did, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:24.03,1:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hold fast. Hold fast! Hold fast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.41,1:16:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir. What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:30.08,1:16:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase! What the devil is it? Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:34.09,1:16:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's been following us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:35.71,1:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:38.13,1:16:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's nothing out there, Mr. Chase! There ain't nothing out there, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:41.18,1:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, what are you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.82,1:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Brace! Brace! Brace!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:00.15,1:17:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.55,1:17:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where is he?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:28.43,1:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This could be Ducie Island.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:30.93,1:19:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Without a map, compass or quadrant, there's no way to be certain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.35,1:19:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We will keep fires going night and day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:37.23,1:19:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hope a passing ship catches sight of our smoke.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:37.20,1:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is what I wanted you to see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:47.59,1:20:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They've been here a long time, no doubt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:50.84,1:20:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Waiting for a ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.55,1:20:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But no ship came.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:57.52,1:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No ship is going to come.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.18,1:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we stay, we die.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:02.69,1:21:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How long do you think it'll take the tropic birds to stop coming here once they see their eggs eaten?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:26.38,1:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's a privilege to know the moment of one's death in advance,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:30.55,1:21:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,be able to prepare for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.76,1:21:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Curse to be so far from home
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:38.01,1:21:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,without a chance to say goodbyes, without a chance to make peace,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:42.69,1:21:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,without a chance to settle the scores.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:47.98,1:21:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then let us at least settle those between us, Captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.57,1:21:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain of what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:56.57,1:21:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex was lost through no fault of yours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:59.66,1:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I was as much to blame for... - You are not the captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:07.54,1:22:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But you were born to do this job.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:10.71,1:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I was just born into it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:25.48,1:22:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do we do, do you think, George?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.15,1:22:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And what offense did we give God to upset him so?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.24,1:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The only creature to have offended God here is the whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:37.03,1:22:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not us?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:40.12,1:22:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In our arrogance, our greed, look where we find ourselves.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:43.75,1:22:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are supreme creatures made in God's own likeness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:47.71,1:22:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Earthly kings
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.59,1:22:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,whose business it is to circumnavigate the planet bestowed to us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:54.01,1:22:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To bend nature to our will.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:56.34,1:22:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You really feel like an earthly king after everything that we've been through?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.31,1:23:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're nothing. We're...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:03.06,1:23:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We're specks. And dust.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.89,1:23:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We sail into the sun at dawn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.23,1:23:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we are to die,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.19,1:23:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then with God's grace,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:14.86,1:23:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,let us die as men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:28.17,1:23:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are we ready, Mr. Weeks?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:29.92,1:23:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:38.26,1:23:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chappel? Mr. Wright?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.30,1:23:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't do it, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:43.93,1:23:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Me, Wrights and Weeks,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:47.02,1:23:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we're staying.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:56.61,1:23:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You ready to go, Matthew?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:09.62,1:24:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I'll give you a hand. Here, you gotta get up. - No, there's no point.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:12.21,1:24:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- You hear me? - No, we're going home. We're going home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:14.55,1:24:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's no point.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.71,1:24:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:22.26,1:24:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God damn it, Matthew.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:27.02,1:24:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:29.35,1:24:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, I'll send a boat for you the minute we get back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:32.06,1:24:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then we'll play cards back in Nantucket, all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:34.65,1:24:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:35.82,1:24:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- It's a deal. - Good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:44.28,1:24:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You want me to open that for you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:50.25,1:24:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.17,1:24:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If it comes to that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:58.55,1:25:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,God be with you, brother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:02.01,1:25:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, and you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:22.53,1:25:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Brother Peterson?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:25.45,1:25:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Y'all coming with us?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.83,1:25:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Peterson. Why don't you come in our boat with Mr. Bond here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:04.57,1:26:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where... Where is he?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:08.20,1:26:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pollard?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:10.66,1:26:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Lawrence. Mr. Lawrence, wake up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:14.75,1:26:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's the other boat gone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:17.33,1:26:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pollard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:18.42,1:26:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Captain Pollard! - Captain Pollard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:20.50,1:26:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.42,1:26:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Pollard. - Captain!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.84,1:26:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:29.22,1:26:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pollard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:35.35,1:26:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's the matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:52.58,1:26:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Benjamin. What are you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:54.75,1:26:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:56.75,1:26:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Putting him overboard, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:00.59,1:27:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look at me. Look at me, Benjamin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.39,1:27:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No right-minded sailor discards what might yet save him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.40,1:27:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Listen to me, boy. Listen to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:29.66,1:27:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He can help us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.99,1:27:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My God. My heavenly king.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:34.16,1:27:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sweetness is the power of his grace.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.75,1:27:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,With longing eyes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:39.42,1:27:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,thy creatures await on thee for daily food.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:43.84,1:27:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My soul is dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.85,1:28:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So it was decided.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:09.11,1:28:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We prepared the body.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:13.99,1:28:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We removed the organs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:18.62,1:28:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Separated his limbs from his body
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:22.96,1:28:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and cut all the flesh from the bones.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:30.01,1:28:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After which,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:32.39,1:28:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we closed the body
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:35.56,1:28:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and we sewed it up
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:37.68,1:28:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,as decently as we could
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:40.23,1:28:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and committed it to the sea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.57,1:28:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We ate the heart first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:54.99,1:28:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You judge me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.75,1:28:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:06.21,1:29:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.26,1:29:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:10.51,1:29:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It is done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:14.26,1:29:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It is out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:17.51,1:29:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you've never told anyone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:21.77,1:29:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:24.77,1:29:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not even your wife?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:27.44,1:29:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you think she could ever love me
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:29.74,1:29:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if she knew the abominations I had committed?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.91,1:29:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. She would.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:36.78,1:29:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And if you had told me the story when we met,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:40.45,1:29:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I would still wear your ring today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:44.96,1:29:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The strength of that boy still lives in you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:51.30,1:29:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:53.63,1:29:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even if you don't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:16.62,1:30:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can finish your story now, my love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:35.18,1:30:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, sit up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:40.18,1:30:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Listen,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.47,1:30:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,put your head back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.48,1:30:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look, we still got a few drops of water left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:49.69,1:30:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't you quit on me. We're going home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.99,1:31:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you have a family back home, Mr. Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:02.04,1:31:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, I have a wife.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:06.96,1:31:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, and a son or a daughter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:54.92,1:31:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Very well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:58.05,1:31:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:59.38,1:32:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We will draw again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.55,1:32:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We will do no such thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:03.39,1:32:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll draw again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:04.93,1:32:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Ramsdell,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:07.18,1:32:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you will assume command of this vessel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.73,1:32:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cousin, will you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:15.94,1:32:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're our... You're our captain. The men need you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:20.20,1:32:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The men will be fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:22.87,1:32:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:24.70,1:32:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please. Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:26.62,1:32:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Henry. - Let us draw again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:29.25,1:32:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It is an order.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:32.58,1:32:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you cannot do it, pass the pistol to another man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:04.07,1:33:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Henry, no, no, no!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:15.42,1:33:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You gotta help me, kid. You gotta help me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.76,1:33:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We were weeks in the doldrums.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:23.84,1:33:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That part of the Pacific is more desert than ocean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:27.51,1:33:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The sun beating down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:30.48,1:33:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My fear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.35,1:33:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All I could think about
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:36.69,1:33:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,was that everyone would die, and I'd be the last left alive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:41.61,1:33:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And as best Mr. Chase could tell, we were still 800 miles from land.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:51.71,1:33:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.38,1:34:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.34,1:34:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am happy to see you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:07.72,1:34:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Been very little happiness in our survival.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:12.31,1:34:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Or in ours, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:15.06,1:34:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Barzillai?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:19.40,1:34:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The third boat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:21.90,1:34:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They've, uh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:24.74,1:34:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They've been gone for days. I'm afraid they're lost, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.61,1:35:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, you have the best position.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:17.79,1:35:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's just a whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:23.21,1:35:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's there! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:26.05,1:35:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Throw it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:31.60,1:35:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Throw it! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:33.47,1:35:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:45.32,1:35:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Throw it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:47.61,1:35:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:57.08,1:36:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Kill it! He's there! Throw the lance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:19.35,1:36:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why didn't you kill it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:47.80,1:36:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're a damn fool.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:13.24,1:37:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Currents drew us apart
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:16.74,1:37:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and that was the last we would see of Captain Pollard's whale boat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:22.92,1:37:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A boat!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:25.34,1:37:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Broad on the port bow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:53.07,1:37:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,May God have mercy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:37.32,1:38:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:42.33,1:38:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:45.92,1:38:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't leave me, Father!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:38.05,1:39:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:40.85,1:39:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:42.22,1:39:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, look. Look, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:48.65,1:39:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:50.73,1:39:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:53.32,1:39:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wake up, Mr. Chase! Here, wake up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:58.24,1:40:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please wake up, sir, there's land.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:01.24,1:40:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:23.01,1:40:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We were rescued there,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:25.10,1:40:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,off the island of Mas Afuera, Chile,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:28.85,1:40:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,90 days after the sinking of the Essex.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:33.27,1:40:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They gave us some old clothes. Fed us, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:38.36,1:40:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was hard to eat at first. Strange.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:43.28,1:40:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They looked after us as best they could
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:45.41,1:40:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,till we found a ship that would carry us home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:49.29,1:40:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That voyage took another three months.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:00.80,1:41:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It looked like the whole island turned out to see us return.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:05.31,1:41:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But there were no cheers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:08.14,1:41:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Only silence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:11.06,1:41:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They looked at us like we were
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:13.27,1:41:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,apparitions,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:15.44,1:41:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,phantoms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:17.78,1:41:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'd said nothing of the details of our survival to anyone,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:21.99,1:41:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but I wondered if they somehow knew of our privations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:26.99,1:41:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maybe they were just curious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:07.87,1:42:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:17.00,1:42:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I promised, didn't I?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:26.97,1:42:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:29.72,1:42:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:32.02,1:42:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, sweetie. Who's this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:35.23,1:42:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Phoebe Ann.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:40.82,1:42:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Phoebe Ann Chase, huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:43.90,1:42:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is Daddy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:47.07,1:42:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, sweetie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:53.87,1:42:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's your daddy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.05,1:43:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:12.89,1:43:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course, they couldn't leave him alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:15.35,1:43:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase and his wife had scarcely walked a block towards home
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:18.61,1:43:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,when he was stopped and made to return to the Maritime office.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:23.03,1:43:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There were business matters still in question.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:39.63,1:43:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, to the matter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:45.80,1:43:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Due to the significant loss of life and property on our voyage,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:50.09,1:43:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it seems there will be an inquiry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:52.81,1:43:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And as captain and first mate, we will be expected to give an account of what happened.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:57.73,1:43:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:59.31,1:44:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And having discussed this with the ship owners
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:02.73,1:44:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and my father,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:04.78,1:44:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it is clear that full disclosure will have ramifications.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:09.07,1:44:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Terrible ramifications for the whole industry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:12.78,1:44:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That a whale brought down the Essex.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:16.45,1:44:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:25.80,1:44:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If the insurance houses and investors were to start worrying about
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:30.18,1:44:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sea monsters sinking ships,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:33.01,1:44:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sailors drawing lots to survive...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:36.98,1:44:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are in the oil business.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:39.44,1:44:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:41.27,1:44:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And as in any business, the probability of success must always be greater than the risk incurred.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:48.53,1:44:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, what are you suggesting, George?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:50.49,1:44:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That you say the ship ran aground.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.03,1:44:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's a lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.87,1:44:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And that the men that died, drowned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:57.12,1:44:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And that's another lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:58.71,1:45:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Think on it. They will make you captain. - Well, that pledge I already have in writing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:02.38,1:45:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Only on the condition you bring home a ship full of oil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:07.88,1:45:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This way, it's guaranteed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:09.55,1:45:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You would be a wealthy man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:12.05,1:45:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The name Chase need no longer be a landsman's name, but an established name
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:16.64,1:45:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that belongs among the great families of Nantucket.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:20.56,1:45:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You want me to whitewash what happened for profit?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:23.73,1:45:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are asking you to be pragmatic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:42.50,1:45:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex was stove by a white whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:45.84,1:45:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And those of us that survived in ill-equipped whaleboats had to commit abominations
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:51.05,1:45:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,in order to survive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:53.09,1:45:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And, on our return, we're expected to spread barefaced lies
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:57.93,1:46:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so that you, the ship owners of Nantucket,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:01.18,1:46:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,might line your pockets and sleep well at night?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:05.27,1:46:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, I will not embroider the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:08.61,1:46:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nor should you, George.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:29.96,1:46:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That last time I saw him...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:32.22,1:46:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Chase, sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:34.38,1:46:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I couldn't find the right words to say what I wanted to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:38.47,1:46:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thomas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:40.60,1:46:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Perhaps there are no words.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:44.98,1:46:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm gonna be on my way to Falmouth and...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:51.15,1:46:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:53.24,1:46:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's been an honor, sir, to sail with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:00.83,1:47:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The honor's been mine, Mr. Nickerson.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:20.51,1:47:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:26.94,1:47:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good luck out there, Thomas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:30.02,1:47:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:00.64,1:48:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next day, George Pollard was called before the inquiry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:08.31,1:48:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gentlemen, Captain George Pollard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:11.15,1:48:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And all the important men in Nantucket were there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:14.82,1:48:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was a formality.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:17.82,1:48:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good day to you, Captain. Please sit down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:25.70,1:48:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For the record, then...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:29.42,1:48:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Essex was stove by a white whale
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:32.21,1:48:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1,200 leagues west of Ecuador.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:34.92,1:48:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was as if Owen Chase himself had spoken.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:39.76,1:48:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Told them the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:45.26,1:48:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Captain Pollard's conscience was clear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:48.94,1:48:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the inquiry was a sham.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:52.94,1:48:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pollard went out again,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:57.40,1:48:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,looking for the white whale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:59.78,1:49:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He never found it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:02.70,1:49:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He ran a second ship aground off Hawaii.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:06.45,1:49:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Twice cursed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:09.46,1:49:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Never sailed again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:11.12,1:49:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And Owen Chase?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:14.25,1:49:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He was a man of his word.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:16.75,1:49:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,First, he sent a boat back to Ducie Island.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:20.55,1:49:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Joy had passed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:22.64,1:49:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the other three were, incredibly, still alive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:29.06,1:49:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:30.98,1:49:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then he packed up his family and moved to New Bedford.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:36.32,1:49:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Started over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:38.65,1:49:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Became a merchant captain,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:40.99,1:49:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sailing on his own terms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:52.50,1:49:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, you certainly got your money's worth, Mr. Melville.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:56.09,1:49:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,These February nights are the longest of the year.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:58.75,1:50:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, you can both rest now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:00.51,1:50:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Believe me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:02.34,1:50:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I shall not be resting for some time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:05.30,1:50:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:07.81,1:50:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You got your story.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:09.52,1:50:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know, your plot. It's all there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:12.81,1:50:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maybe it wasn't a plot I was after.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:16.69,1:50:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No. What, then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:18.73,1:50:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Something else you've given me tonight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:21.44,1:50:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And what's that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:23.78,1:50:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The courage to go where
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:26.03,1:50:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,one does not want to go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:29.79,1:50:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Melville,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:31.95,1:50:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,what you've heard, what I've told you,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:37.63,1:50:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,will it all be of service to your book?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:43.22,1:50:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It will be a work of fiction, Mr. Nickerson,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.85,1:50:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,inspired by truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:50.97,1:50:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I don't believe I'll feel the need to use all of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:03.36,1:51:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Thank you. - Here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:05.32,1:51:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take that with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:06.24,1:51:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No. The money is for you. I insist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:09.83,1:51:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I insist you keep it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:11.54,1:51:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And I insist one person in this conversation is sober.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:26.18,1:51:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So it's back to, uh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:27.51,1:51:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Pittsfield, Massachusetts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:29.89,1:51:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:33.27,1:51:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:37.94,1:51:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You know,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:40.02,1:51:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I heard a man from Pennsylvania drilled a hole in the ground recently
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:44.57,1:51:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and found oil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:46.78,1:51:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That can't be true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:48.95,1:51:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I heard it, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:52.45,1:51:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oil from the ground.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:56.58,1:51:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Fancy that.


